headline: Morgan Stanley raises China 2025 GDP growth forecast
summary: Wall Street firm MorganStanley raised its 2025 GDP growth forecast for China by50 bps to 4.5%, citing the impact of stimulus measures on localgovernments and consumption that have started to filter...

headline: BlackRock Low Duration Bond Fund Q4 2024 Review
